      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be roadworthy again. The engine has trouble idling, the transmission slips intermittently, and there is visible rust damage on the body panels along with a heavily worn interior. It is best suited as a project car for an enthusiast or as a source for parts, and it is recommended that the buyer hauls it away rather than driving it off the lot.",
