    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so excited for whoever ends up with this absolute gem! It is in truly stunning condition\u2014I've babied this car since the day I got it, and it seriously looks like it belongs in a showroom. It drives like a total dream and the interior is still looking (and smelling!) brand new. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I do. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
